 the United States" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Publication</div><div class="teaser-topic">Cold War</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">From Mao to Deng: China’s Changing Relations with the United States</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Chen Jian</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="external" href="https://digitalarchive.wilsoncenter.org/collection/156/berlin-wall" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><div class="teaser-image"><picture title="AP Images"><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/images/external/berlin_wall_ap.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/images/external/berlin_wall_ap.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="AP images" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">External link</div><div class="teaser-topic">Cold War</div></div><div class="teaser-title -external"><span class="teaser-title-text">Fall of the Wall at 30</span></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="site-footer-top"><div class="site-footer-top-inner"><div class="site-footer-column"><a class="site-footer-logo" href="/"><img src="/themes/custom/wilson/assets/images/footer-logo.svg" alt="Wilson Center" width="100%" height="auto"></a><p class="site-footer-location -serif">One Woodrow Wilson Plaza<br>1300 Pennsylvania Ave. NW<br>Washington, DC 20004-3027</p><a class="site-footer-visit" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Wilson+Center/@38.8934628,-77.0325588,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89b7b79762f518d1:0x3e73088a9489b574!8m2!3d38.8934586!4d-77.0303701" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Visit the Wilson Center</a><div class="site-footer-phone"